Install Bash Update Script

curl -s https://raw.github.com/nandub/sublime2-selfupdate/master/sl2update > sl2

chmod 755 sl2

sudo cp -p sl2 /usr/local/bin

Update Sublime Text 2

sl2 -b 2126 -l $HOME/devtools -BIP

usage: sl2 options

Sublime Text 2 build installer.

OPTIONS:
   -h      Show this message
   -b      Specify build number
   -l      Location to install. default: /Users/fortiz/Applications on Mac OS X or /Users/fortiz/development/tools/sublime2-selfupdate on Linux (TODO)
   -B      Install the Sublime Text 2 TextMate Bundle
   -I      Install a better icon.
   -P      Install the Sublime Text 2 Package Control Manager

